.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>不管是什麼類型的工程師，都必須跟終端機(Terminal)好好相處，查看目錄<code>ls</code>我想是大家第一個學的Unix指令，以下是我常用的用法。</p></blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"ls-基本用法\"><a href=\"#ls-基本用法\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"ls 基本用法\"></a>ls 基本用法</h1><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">ls</span> <span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><img src=\"../../images/f69b45f945fc1f1306866ea973ca61eeb4508d0364038697045f2462ba1cb700.png\" alt=\"ls 基本用法\">  </p>\n<h1 id=\"以清單模式顯示\"><a href=\"#以清單模式顯示\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"以清單模式顯示\"></a>以清單模式顯示</h1><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">ls</span> -l<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><img src=\"../../images/00a6c6f865c97f6b6a43fc90df4c9f183d20a3c3dda5099ffe1b4bad8e7fb2d5.png\" alt=\"以清單模式顯示\">  </p>\n<h1 id=\"顯示隱藏檔案\"><a href=\"#顯示隱藏檔案\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"顯示隱藏檔案\"></a>顯示隱藏檔案</h1><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">ls</span> -a<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><img src=\"../../images/deefc4eb3c3e957ef3a193b80904e99521153b1a287b2bdcd1a689ee40df88e4.png\" alt=\"顯示隱藏檔案\">  </p>\n<h1 id=\"以時間排序\"><a href=\"#以時間排序\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"以時間排序\"></a>以時間排序</h1><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">ls</span> -ltr<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><img src=\"../../images/16119d3502a26a2108c7eccef4fe8ffed7d2aec790d4ec8a6b922212b3ac9da7.png\" alt=\"以時間排序\">  </p>\n<h1 id=\"以檔案大小排序\"><a href=\"#以檔案大小排序\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"以檔案大小排序\"></a>以檔案大小排序</h1><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">ls</span> -lS<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><img src=\"../../images/34eadbfa2e1241f59eb0a8f1dfc64e6fbc2764632371c9e2bb9437503a1ef15a.png\" alt=\"以檔案大小排序\">  </p>\n<p>想知道更多關於: <a href=\"https://man7.org/linux/man-pages/man1/ls.1.html\">ls</a></p>\n","feature":true,"text":" 不管是什麼類型的工程師，都必須跟終端機(Terminal)好好相處，查看目錄ls我想是大家第一個學的Unix指令，以下是我常用的用法。 ls 基本用法$ ls 以清單模式顯示$ ls -l 顯示隱藏檔案$ ls -a 以時間排序$ ls -ltr 以檔案大小排序$ ls -lS...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":177,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"Devops","slug":"Devops","count":2,"path":"api/categories/Devops.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Windows","slug":"Windows","count":2,"path":"api/tags/Windows.json"},{"name":"Mac","slug":"Mac","count":2,"path":"api/tags/Mac.json"},{"name":"Unix","slug":"Unix","count":2,"path":"api/tags/Unix.json"},{"name":"Bash","slug":"Bash","count":2,"path":"api/tags/Bash.json"},{"name":"遇到問題就解決","slug":"遇到問題就解決","count":2,"path":"api/tags/遇到問題就解決.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#ls-%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E7%94%A8%E6%B3%95\"><span class=\"toc-text\">ls 基本用法</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BB%A5%E6%B8%85%E5%96%AE%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%E9%A1%AF%E7%A4%BA\"><span class=\"toc-text\">以清單模式顯示</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E9%A1%AF%E7%A4%BA%E9%9A%B1%E8%97%8F%E6%AA%94%E6%A1%88\"><span class=\"toc-text\">顯示隱藏檔案</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BB%A5%E6%99%82%E9%96%93%E6%8E%92%E5%BA%8F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">以時間排序</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BB%A5%E6%AA%94%E6%A1%88%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%8F%E6%8E%92%E5%BA%8F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">以檔案大小